advertisingDetails.name: Sponsored Display
advertisingDetails.hint: Sponsored Display is a self-service advertising solution that gives advertisers the ability to quickly launch display campaigns and reach relevant audiences across the shopping journey, on and off Amazon.

advertisingDetails.name: Sponsored Brands
advertisingDetails.hint: Sponsored Brands costs are assigned to products advertised in the campaign in relation to total product's sales (including organic sales) in a given period. If there were no sales, the costs are distributed evenly among all products in the campaign.
